      "content": "it’s weird being out here. i can walk through these crowded streets for hours and feel like i’m literally a ghost. like, if i just stopped showing up tomorrow, the world wouldn't even glitch. it's just a zero-sum game. i take up space, i consume resources, but there's zero net impact on anything. i'm just... background noise.",
